<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="1Jun1934"><font color="red">1 June 1934</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Lucia Joyce): Today at last I have been able to send off the [<i>Mime</i>] &hellip; Let me know if the book pleases you. I like it very much. Lord knows what my prose means. In a word, it is pleasing to the ear. </div>
